    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさん、どうやって鼻を明かすつもりなんだろう）\n（……いやいや、俺が期待してどうするんだ）",
      "startTime": 64.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tenniscourt-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "え、練習だけじゃなくて、試合もやるんですか？\nミニゲームみたいなものだから、気楽にやっていい？",
      "startTime": 73.2897280373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "うー、kanaホームランを打ってばっかりだったし\n大丈夫かなぁ、一点も取れなかったらどうしよう",
      "startTime": 81.7897280373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tenniscourt-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tenniscourt-00-noon.webp",
