      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（また……速い！　あ、でもギリギリで返したな）\n（でも、そんなヘロヘロ球では、kanaさんが……！）",
      "startTime": 129.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "やった、またkanaの得点！！\nえーと、点の数え方は……30でいいんだったかな",
      "startTime": 136.2395016883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
