      "text": "さ、どんどん行くよー！！\n次は、さっき習ったやり方でサーブ打ってみようっと",
      "startTime": 144.4191610969,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fishing-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3133.3333332999873,
          "startTime": 147.5524944302
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_tennis-03.m4a",
          "delay": 3347.505569799978,
          "startTime": 147.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（ま、またもや、目にも留まらぬ速さ！！）\n（コロ子選手、もう完全に腰が引けている！！）",
      "startTime": 152.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_09_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "コロ子ちゃん、ほら、立って立って！\nまだ試合は終わってないんだからね、次行くよ～！",
      "startTime": 158.4870521542,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fishing-01.m4a",
